descriptions: Concordance Healthcare Solutions is a healthcare supply chain management company that offers a comprehensive range of products and services to healthcare providers, ensuring streamlined procurement processes and efficient delivery of medical supplies.
Trinity Sterile Inc is a medical device company that specializes in the manufacturing and distribution of sterile medical products, ensuring safety and quality in healthcare facilities.

Kerma Medical Products is a healthcare company that manufactures and distributes radiation protection and patient positioning products for medical imaging and radiation therapy, ensuring precision and safety in healthcare procedures.

Zimmer Biomet Inc is a global leader in the design, manufacturing, and distribution of orthopedic and musculoskeletal medical devices and technologies, providing innovative solutions to improve patient outcomes and quality of life.

Aurora Spine Inc is a medical technology company that focuses on the development and commercialization of innovative spinal implant solutions for the treatment of spinal disorders, providing advanced options for improved patient outcomes.
